Why connect my Google account?

Linking your Google account allows you to activate PayPal One Touch™, so you’ll speed through check-out without having to log in every time. You can always opt out later in Settings at PayPal.com.

Whenever you’re logged in with your Google account, you can speed through checkout without typing your password.

Stay logged in for faster checkout

Skip typing your password by staying logged in on this device. For security, we'll occasionally ask you to log in, including every time you update your personal or financial info. We don't recommend using One TouchTM on shared devices. Turn this off at any time in your PayPal settings.
